<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Virtual Lost and Found</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/08/97/11/03/240_F_897110304_UzSVoLcNBrra1cwdh9dK5Ma8pSw5Qope.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.8);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .main-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .info-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .info-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
        }

        .option-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .option-card {
            flex: 1;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .option-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .option-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .option-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 15px 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .option-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin: 0 15px 20px;
        }

        .option-card button {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: #34495E;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .option-card button:hover {
            background: #2C3E50;
        }

        footer {
            background: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.8);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        footer button {
            background: #ECF0F1;
            color: #2C3E50;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer button:hover {
            background: #BDC3C7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Virtual Lost and Found</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the platform that helps you find and report lost items with ease.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>About Our Service</h2>
            <p>

                "This platform allows you to report items you have found, search for your lost belongings, and assist in reuniting lost items with their rightful owners."</p>
        </div>

        <div class="option-container">
            <div class="option-card">
                <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1074499974/photo/woman-found-lost-leather-wallet.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=INDYEtJ5oQ67Q-kFUksLjJBohh0c9s3qs6pQVA_o758=" alt="Report Lost Item">
                <h3>Report a Lost Item</h3>
                <p>"Provide details of an item you have found, to assist in its recovery."</p>
                <button onclick="location.href='/report-lost'">Get Started</button>
            </div>
            <div class="option-card">
                <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/2003069481/photo/travel-concept.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=4SKbMdM3UYwjkiJxH59O-L8XzngffCK-Rtr05Eci0io=" alt="Search Lost Item">
                <h3>Search for Lost Items</h3>
                <p>Browse through reported items and find what you lost.</p>
                <button onclick="location.href='/search-lost'">Search Now</button>
            </div>
            <div class="option-card">
                <img src="https://deliverback.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/report-a-lost-item-768x768.png" alt="View Reported Items">
                <h3>View My Reports</h3>
                <p>"Check and manage the items you have reported so far"</p>
                <button onclick="location.href='/my-lost-items'">View Reports</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
            <h2>Safety Tips</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide accurate information about lost or found items.</li>
                <li>Meet in public places for exchanges to stay safe.</li>
                <li>Report items promptly for better chances of recovery.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Virtual Lost and Found | All Rights Reserved</p>
        <button onclick="location.href='/logout'">Logout</button>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
